                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#59a14f' fontname='Tw Cen MT Condensed Extra Bold' fontsize='16' italic='true' underline='true'>Insights</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#59a14f' fontsize='12'>* Sales fluctuate across months with a noticeable mid-year dip</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#59a14f' fontsize='12'>* Certain categories contribute more significantly to total sales</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
