          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#005300' fontsize='20'>* Sales and profit performance varies significantly across product categories</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#005300' fontsize='20'>* A small set of customers contributes disproportionately to total sales</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#005300' fontsize='20'>* Higher discount levels tend to impact profitability across multiple orders</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#005300' fontsize='20'>* Shipping mode plays a role in overall profit performance</run>
          </formatted-text>
